# Design system

All pages and components should feel **futuristic, sleek, minimal, and modern**.

## Visual language

- Dark-friendly glass surfaces: `bg-base-200/40`, `backdrop-blur-xl`, subtle borders (`border-base-content/8`)
- Soft primary glow accents — never loud gradients or heavy shadows
- Fine grid backgrounds and blurred orbs for depth (see login page)
- Rounded corners: `rounded-lg` for controls, `rounded-2xl` for cards
- Typography: tight tracking on headings, muted `text-base-content/40–60` for secondary text

## Components

- Use `lucide-react` via `@fuel-carrier/web-ui/icons` in apps — no per-app `lucide-react` dependency
- Prefer shared primitives from `@fuel-carrier/web-ui` (Button, Input, PanelShell)
- Minimal chrome — every element should earn its place
- Consistent spacing scale (`gap-4`, `p-6`, `px-4 lg:px-8`)
- Smooth transitions: `transition-all` on interactive elements

## Layout

- Authenticated pages use `PanelShell` with side navigation
- Public pages (login) stay full-screen centered
- Mobile-first responsive; side nav collapses to drawer on small screens
